OL,3,CInvest in childhood 'or risk losing a
OL,4,Cgeneration to poor mental health'
OL,6,FThe Government must "invest in
OL,7,Fchildhood" or risk losing the next
OL,8,Fgeneration to poor mental health, a
OL,9,Fcharity has warned.
OL,11,FA new report by the Centre for Mental
OL,12,FHealth said poor mental health as a
OL,13,Fchild "casts a long shadow into the
OL,14,Ffuture", and can often lead chronic
OL,15,Fmental and physical health issues in
OL,16,Fadulthood.
