OL,3,CInvest in childhood 'or risk losing a
OL,4,Cgeneration to poor mental health'
OL,6,FIt also claims preventing mental
OL,7,Fhealth issues is "highly cost-
OL,8,Feffective", and a proactive approach
OL,9,Fby the Government "can significantly
OL,10,Fimprove mental health outcomes and
OL,11,Fgenerate substantial economic savings".
OL,13,FThe report, Invest in Childhood, said
OL,14,Fmental health is a "critical issue for
OL,15,Fbabies, children and young people".
OL,17,FAccording to NHS data, about one in
OL,18,Ffive children and young adults aged
OL,19,Feight to 25 in England had a probable
OL,20,Fmental disorder in 2023.
