OL,3,CInvest in childhood 'or risk losing a
OL,4,Cgeneration to poor mental health'
OL,6,FThis included about a fifth of eight
OL,7,Fto 16-year-olds, almost a quarter
OL,8,F(23.3%) of 17 to 19-year-olds and
OL,9,F21.7% of 20 to 25-year-olds.
OL,11,FThe charity calls for a "whole system
OL,12,Fpreventative approach to mental
OL,13,Fhealth" that "could yield substantial
OL,14,Fsavings by addressing issues before
OL,15,Fthey escalate into more severe
OL,16,Fproblems".
OL,18,FThis would involve integrating sectors
OL,19,Fsuch as education, healthcare, social
OL,20,Fcare and community organisations, the
OL,21,Freport said.
