OL,3,CInvest in childhood 'or risk losing a
OL,4,Cgeneration to poor mental health'
OL,6,FIt highlights six areas that require
OL,7,Faction, including providing effective
OL,8,Fmental health support during pregnancy
OL,9,Fand early parenthood, and bringing in
OL,10,Fpolicies focusing on tackling inter-
OL,11,Fgenerational trauma, particularly in
OL,12,Ffamilies that have experienced racism.
OL,14,FElsewhere, the report said early years
OL,15,Fchildcare, schools and colleges "play
OL,16,Fa vital role" in promoting good mental
OL,17,Fhealth, while secure housing and
OL,18,Femployment are "crucial" for young
OL,19,Fadults.
