OL,3,CInvest in childhood 'or risk losing a
OL,4,Cgeneration to poor mental health'
OL,6,FAndy Bell, chief executive at Centre
OL,7,Ffor Mental Health, said: "Mental
OL,8,Fhealth difficulties among children and
OL,9,Fyoung people are both common and
OL,10,Fserious.
OL,12,F"They cause deep distress for children
OL,13,Fand their families. They cast a long
OL,14,Fshadow over a child's life."
