OL,3,CInvest in childhood 'or risk losing a
OL,4,Cgeneration to poor mental health'
OL,6,FAmong the recommendations laid out in
OL,7,Fthe report is a call for the
OL,8,FGovernment to tackle the "social
OL,9,Fdeterminants" of children's mental
OL,10,Fhealth by taking action in areas such
OL,11,Fas child poverty and violence against
OL,12,Fwomen and girls.
OL,14,FIt also calls for investment in
OL,15,Fcommunity mental health promotion,
OL,16,Fevidence-based parenting programmes,
OL,17,Fimproving mental health support for
OL,18,Fnew mothers, and expanding the health
OL,19,Fvisitor and school nurse workforce.
