OL,3,CInvest in childhood 'or risk losing a
OL,4,Cgeneration to poor mental health'
OL,6,FIt comes as previous analysis by the
OL,7,FCentre for Mental Health showed the
OL,8,Fimpact of childhood mental health
OL,9,Fproblems could lead to #1 trillion in
OL,10,Flost earnings across the generation.
OL,12,FMr Bell said: "Preventing mental
OL,13,Fhealth problems is highly cost-
OL,14,Feffective. It saves money and lives.
OL,15,FOur report identifies actions the
OL,16,FGovernment can take now to shift
OL,17,Ftowards prevention.
OL,26,@tD@OOU
