OL,6,F"We have already announced #26 million
OL,7,Fto open new mental health crisis
OL,8,Fcentres, are recruiting 8,500
OL,9,Fadditional mental health workers and
OL,10,Fputting a specialist mental health
OL,11,Fprofessional in every school in
OL,12,FEngland.
OL,14,F"Through our Plan for Change, we will
OL,15,Fraise the healthiest generation of
OL,16,Fchildren in our history by reforming
OL,17,Fthe NHS to give mental health the same
OL,18,Fattention and focus as physical
OL,19,Fhealth."
